title: After a Sugar High of Free Money, These Billion-Dollar Technologies Need a Nap
description: Once overhyped and overpromised, these major areas of tech investment are finally facing reality. The contraction and disinvestment may only be just beginning.

title: Why Does Anybody Need 37 Stanley Cups?
description: People are spending thousands of dollars to have Stanley tumblers and Lululemon hoodies in different colors. Blame—or thank—social media.
